the same DNA in them.

00:04:39.070 --> 00:04:41.210
And it's the
instructions in that DNA

00:04:41.210 --> 00:04:45.506
that make your cells do what
they do and build your body.

00:04:45.506 --> 00:04:46.880
So this is the
key thing to know.

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:48.430
When people start
talking about genes

00:04:48.430 --> 00:04:51.510
