copied and copied and copied.

00:11:06.620 --> 00:11:11.340
Your genome is basically, a
lot of the time, full of crap.

00:11:11.340 --> 00:11:13.870
And some of it is
actively harmful.

00:11:13.870 --> 00:11:15.850
Some of it is garbage.

00:11:15.850 --> 00:11:17.230
We have some things
in our genome

00:11:17.230 --> 00:11:20.160
that are really not good for
us, and evolution is gradually

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:21.980
clearing them out away.

00:11:21.980 --> 00:11:23.970
But a lot of the other
stuff, the junk that's

00:11:23.970 --> 00:11:25.980
in our genome, people say, well,
