00:25:10.440 --> 00:25:13.670
But one single
change in a control

00:25:13.670 --> 00:25:16.230
switch that turns a gene
on at the right time

00:25:16.230 --> 00:25:20.570
to build the pelvis in the
sea sticklebacks, broken

00:25:20.570 --> 00:25:22.660
in the freshwater sticklebacks.

00:25:22.660 --> 00:25:23.650
No pelvis.

00:25:23.650 --> 00:25:24.620
No pelvis at all.

00:25:24.620 --> 00:25:25.120
Gone.

00:25:25.120 --> 00:25:25.619
Vanished.

00:25:25.619 --> 00:25:26.740
Gone.

00:25:26.740 --> 00:25:28.490
It's absolutely incredible.

00:25:28.490 --> 00:25:31.920
And what's even more
amazing is that you

00:25:31.920 --> 00:25:36.160
can take that bit, that
control switch in the DNA,

00:25:36.160 --> 00:25:39.590
