00:36:12.300 --> 00:36:13.026
And you said we're quite--

00:36:13.026 --> 00:36:13.390
KAT ARNEY: Genes.

00:36:13.390 --> 00:36:13.910
MALE SPEAKER: Genes.

00:36:13.910 --> 00:36:14.300
